textBeforeTable: CLICK ON LINKS BELOW TO VIEW OR DOWNLOAD Warranty: One-year limited Length: 6' Frame Material: 2 3/8" O.D. pipe Plank Material: Recycled plastic supported by steel bars Specifications Backed by a one-year warranty Made in the USA Each plank is reinforced with flat steel bars to prevent sagging Planks are made of 100 percent recycled plastic UltraSite's Recycled Plastic Bench without Back is more than attractive and affordable outdoor seating. Each of the planks is made of 100 percent recycled plastic that won't rust, chip or scratch like traditional materials, making the bench an investment you can feel good about. The planks are reinforced with flat steel bars that prevent sagging and are supported by a welded steel frame. Available as a portable, surface mount or in ground mount bench.
